reviewText: I was a teenager in the late 50's and this movie was typical of that time.  The music was good as well as the plot of the movie.

this is a review of vhs purchase which was bran new, never opened, the picture quality is a 10, crisp B&W, the film with a story line so so but the real film is the singers in all their splendor, the sound was clear and strong, great music for baby boomers like me.
